    IsClosed (closure (interior (A : Set X)) âˆª closure (interior (B : Set X))) := by
  have hA : IsClosed (closure (interior (A : Set X))) := isClosed_closure
  have hB : IsClosed (closure (interior (B : Set X))) := isClosed_closure
